dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Oh, you're up.
The child speaks plainly.
If it weren't for the visceral scenery, it could be mistaken for a cordial greeting to someone who just woke up from a sweet slumber.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Good thing you got up in time. If the work's done while the heartbeat's too slow, it impacts the taste.
The child watches someone laid on the floor with a light cackle.
The pitiful fellow writhes and struggles on the floor, unable to accept the situation they're in.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: 어이, 너무 움직이지 마. 쯧, 그 녀석 한테 적당히 숨을 죽여 놓으라고 말했건만.
Slap.
The child slapped the fellow's cheek, her words heartless.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: I can't stand it when the subject material tries to take the center of the art on its own. Be still if you don't want your L.B.
Even though there was no way for the victim to know that it stood for "limbs broken"...
They noticed quickly enough that being still was the only way to prolong their life.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Here's your reward for being an O.P.
Prick.
The child jabbed a syringe she'd been fiddling with into the victim.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: It's an injection of anesthetic mixed with a variety of flavoring agents. A pricey concoction that will make you the greatest work in the Backstreets, a delicacy...and art.
The child's constant rambling about art and such can be a bit confusing...
One thing to note is that the Backstreets of District 23 are known as the streets of flavor.
That's right. The Backstreets located around the Nest where W Corp is.
Its culture revolves around gastronomy; the people seek good eating and derive beauty from it.
Those closely related to the culinary art, such as the Eight Chefs and the Dochelin Guides, also originate from this place.
This child wants to join the ranks of the prestigious Eight. By using humans, often called one of the flowering pinnacles of artistic cuisine, as her main ingredient.
To that end, the child set up an establish here, and named it R.B. ...The acronyms must be the child's adamant preference.
As one could expect, the child makes pies out of meat. Her pies have been earning a certain kind of reputation among gourmets.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Now... You can feel your senses numbing, yes?
The child delightfully watched her victim as she examined her blade.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: 좋은 소재여야 할 거야. 그레고르, 그 덜떨어지고 어리숙하고 경험도적은 조수랑 작당하는 것도 슬슬 부아가 치밀거든.
Clicking her tongue, the child began to grumble.
Going on about how she dislikes her assistance's sluggish pace, tendency to bring her bad ingredients, dull cleaver damaging the goods, and so on...

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Well, whatever, I'll fire him the moment I rise to one of the Eight Chefs.
While the child complains, the victim's eyelids begin to close.
Why is she so annoyed, what will become of them... Their thoughts blur away, and their consciousness dims.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Hmph, back to work for now.

dataList.title: District 23 Backstreets
dataList.content: Now... Smile. You're about to be at the center of an art piece.
Looking into the victim, the child raises her knife.
Was it a coincidence that the stains of blood on the knife resembled a grin?
...Looking at her face, it looks like there is no need to wonder after all.
